===Noun===
'''whig'''
#[[acidulate|Acidulated]] [[whey]], sometimes mixed with buttermilk and sweet herbs, used as a cooling [[beverage]].
#[[Buttermilk]].
#Variation of ''[[wig]]''.

[[Category:English nouns]]

===Verb===
'''whig'''
#''(transitive)'' [[Urge]] forward; drive [[briskly]].
#''(intransitive)'' [[Jog]] along; move or work briskly.

